# Quick Cheat Sheet

| Operation | Meaning | Result |
|------------|------------|------------|
| `n << 1` | Multiply by 2 | `n × 2` |
| `n << 2` | Multiply by 4 | `n × 4` |
| `n << k` | Multiply by 2ᵏ | `n × 2^k` |
| `n >> 1` | Divide by 2 | `n / 2` |
| `n >> 2` | Divide by 4 | `n / 4` |
| `n >> k` | Divide by 2ᵏ | `n / 2^k` |

---

# Java Program

```java
public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int n = 5;

        System.out.println(n << 1); // 10
        System.out.println(n << 2); // 20

        System.out.println(20 >> 1); // 10
        System.out.println(20 >> 2); // 5
    }
}
```

