# Brian Kernighan Algorithm

Count set bits efficiently.

```java
int count = 0;

while(n != 0)
{
    n = n & (n - 1);
    count++;
}
```

Time Complexity:

```text
O(Number of Set Bits)
```

Better than checking all 32 bits.

